column5: If we got 6 grandmas and put them on the ice wearing Leaf jerseys...they'd beat the Sens.
Ha ha ha, sure looked like that last night...BUT....I am sure all the Sens fans will be the ones laughing come playoff time......
They might laugh at the start of the playoffs, but they know and we all know how it will end...NO CUP
I think it will end the same way for the leafs too.....
